#: lib/tuist_web/marketing/controllers/marketing_html/about.html.heex:63
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "We believe openness builds better tools, keeping only what’s needed closed for sustainable development."
msgstr "オープンネスがより良いツールを生み、持続可能な開発のために必要なものだけを閉じると信じています。"

#: lib/tuist_web/marketing/controllers/marketing_html/about.html.heex:105
